"2  (4-ounce) beef tenderloin steaks","1/4 teaspoon salt","1/8 teaspoon cracked black pepper","6  large sea scallops","1/4 teaspoon crushed pink peppercorns","1 tablespoon olive oil, divided","1/3 cup Champagne or dry white wine","1 1/2 teaspoons fresh lemon juice","1 tablespoon minced shallots","3 tablespoons butter, cut into pieces"